statement:
select
    count(*) as aggregate
from
    `crm_activity` as `activity`
    left join `crm_status` as `status` on `status`.`id` = `activity`.`status`
    left join `crm_category` as `category` on `category`.`id` = `activity`.`category`
    left join `crm_activity_dynamic_data` as `activity_dynamic` on `activity_dynamic`.`activity_id` = `activity`.`id`
    left join `crm_opportunities` as `deal` on `deal`.`id` = `activity`.`opporid`
    left join `crm_deal_dynamic_data` as `deal_dynamic` on `deal_dynamic`.`oppor_id` = `activity`.`opporid`
    left join `crm_customer_details` as `customer` on `customer`.`id` = `activity`.`customer_id`
    left join `crm_customer_dynamic_data` as `customer_dynamic` on `customer_dynamic`.`customer_id` = `activity`.`customer_id`
where
    `activity`.`parentid` = 1575
    and activity.seq_no IS NOT NULL
    and `activity`.`end_datetime` >= 2022 -12 -01
    and `activity`.`datetime` <= 2022 -12 -31
    and `activity`.`id` in (
        select
            `mapping`.`activity_id` as `id`
        from
            `crm_activity_asset_mapping` as `mapping`
            left join `crm_reference` as `asset` on `asset`.`id` = `mapping`.`asset_id`
            left join `crm_reference_dynamic_data` as `asset_dynamic` on `asset_dynamic`.`reference_id` = `mapping`.`asset_id`
        where
            `asset`.`parentid` = 1575
            and `asset`.`category` in (46982)
    )
    and `activity`.`id` in (
        select
            `permission`.`ref_id` as `id`
        from
            `crm_user_permissions` as `permission`
        where
            `permission`.`parentid` = 1575
            and (
                (
                    `permission`.`type` = 'activity'
                    and `permission`.`current_permission` != 0
                    and `permission`.`profileid` = 1575
                )
                or (
                    `permission`.`deal_id` in (
                        select
                            `parentpermission`.`ref_id` as `deal_id`
                        from
                            `crm_user_permissions` as `parentpermission`
                        where
                            `parentpermission`.`parentid` = 1575
                            and (
                                `parentpermission`.`type` = 'deal'
                                and `parentpermission`.`current_permission` != 0
                                and `parentpermission`.`profileid` = 1575
                            )
                    )
                )
                or (
                    `permission`.`customer_id` in (
                        select
                            `parentpermission`.`ref_id` as `customer_id`
                        from
                            `crm_user_permissions` as `parentpermission`
                        where
                            `parentpermission`.`parentid` = 1575
                            and (
                                `parentpermission`.`type` = 'customer'
                                and `parentpermission`.`current_permission` != 0
                                and `parentpermission`.`profileid` = 1575
                            )
                    )
                )
            )
    )
    and `activity`.`isactive` = 1
